- Use utility-first approach for styling components
- Create custom components using `@apply` directive for reusability
- Utilize responsive design utilities for mobile-first development
- Implement dark mode support using Tailwind's dark mode classes
- Use Tailwind's JIT (Just-In-Time) mode for better performance and smaller bundle sizes